reviewText: I'm never disappointed by the Punany Poets!  Jessica Holter always fulfills & satisfies. . .Black Love American Style gives an inside, erotic view of the talent that IS the Punany Poets!  I've followed their performances through 3 different states and have collected several books of poetry and vids!  If you want to learn about the Punany Poets before you SEE the Punany Poets, this is an excellent opportunity.  After you see the vid, you'll want to reserve your tickets for an upcoming performance!
